Every Little Thing

Taken from his first solo album, Armchair Theatre, released in June 1990, the single became a minor hit (#59) in the UK and at #9 on Billboard's Mainstream Rock Tracks chart in the US. It charted at #24 in Australia. Fellow Traveling Wilburys George Harrison and Tom Petty made cameo appearances in the music video, directed by Meiert Avis that received rotation on VH1 at the time.

